    "en": {
      "title": "Indian troops in Sri Lanka: India denies",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Indian High Commission has stated that it completely rejects the media and social media reports that India is sending its troops to Sri Lanka.",
        "The High Commission of India also pointed out that the statements and opinions published on social media are not related to the position of the Government of India. (a)"
      ],
